== Spanish ==
===Adjective===
'''embarazada''' ''f''

#[[pregnant]]

====Usage notes====
*'''Embarazada''' is a [[false friend]], and does not mean "embarrassed".  The word for "embarrassed" in Spanish is ''[[avergonzado]]'' (or "avergonzada" in the feminine form).

